      "text": "ベニテングタケ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772898853,
      "updated": 1772898853
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4c3a0000000000475837",
      "text": "テングタケ科テングタケ属の[毒キノコ]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899387,
      "updated": 1772899388
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4b3b0000000000475831",
      "text": "　赤い傘に白いイボが特徴",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899131,
      "updated": 1772899360
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4b440000000000475832",
      "text": "　　だが、イボが無いこともあるので注意",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899141,
      "updated": 1772899361
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4b690000000000475833",
      "text": "　　イボは擦ると取れてしまう程度のもの",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899178,
      "updated": 1772899363
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4bda0000000000475834",
      "text": "　食用の[タマゴタケ]と間違われやすいことが厚労省の資料でも指摘されている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899290,
      "updated": 1772899312
    },
    {
      "id": "69ac4bf00000000000475835",
      "text": "　　https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/seisakunitsuite/bunya/0000142728.html",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772899312,
      "updated": 1772899323
    },
    {
